name: Genesis Land Development Corp.
longDescription: Genesis Land Development Corp is a Canada-based land developer and home builder. The company is engaged in the acquisition, development, and sale of land, residential lots and homes mainly in the greater Calgary area. The company has two business segments: Land development and Homebuilding. It earns the majority of its revenue from the home building segment.
